14:19.108 --> 14:22.069
That babysitting has turned

14:19.108 --> 14:22.069
into a full-time job.

14:22.111 --> 14:24.823
Well, sometimes I just

14:22.111 --> 14:24.823
go over there to hang out

14:24.864 --> 14:26.783
and watch TV.

14:26.825 --> 14:28.909
Live in a house.

14:28.951 --> 14:32.913
Dad, does this seem okay to you?

14:32.955 --> 14:34.915
Gosh, no.

14:32.955 --> 14:34.915
Your mother and I

14:34.957 --> 14:36.543
have never fought

14:34.957 --> 14:36.543
