14:36.584 --> 14:38.919
It's been days, and we

14:36.584 --> 14:38.919
still haven't made up.

14:38.961 --> 14:40.921
I don't even know

14:38.961 --> 14:40.921
what the problem is.

14:40.963 --> 14:43.924
Nah, something's missing.

14:43.966 --> 14:45.926
Boy...

14:45.968 --> 14:47.928
