14:47.970 --> 14:50.014
Just think,

14:50.056 --> 14:54.853
somewhere out there

14:50.056 --> 14:54.853
in all those stars and planets,

14:54.894 --> 14:58.147
there might be

14:54.894 --> 14:58.147
at this very moment

14:58.189 --> 15:01.735
a space dad

14:58.189 --> 15:01.735
who just got kicked out

15:01.776 --> 15:03.653
of his space trailer,

15:03.695 --> 15:05.363
who's looking down at us.

15:05.405 --> 15:09.033
Or would it be up at us?

15:09.075 --> 15:11.578
Or maybe sideways?

15:11.619 --> 15:15.164
Trust me, Dad.

15:11.619 --> 15:15.164
They're all looking down on us.

15:16.457 --> 15:17.958
The matinee

15:16.457 --> 15:17.958
