15:19.878 --> 15:22.839
Okay. What do you want me

15:19.878 --> 15:22.839
to feed the kids for lunch?

15:22.881 --> 15:23.964
Hmm, whatever you want.

15:24.006 --> 15:25.007
We trust you.

15:25.049 --> 15:26.967
They trust me!

15:27.009 --> 15:28.969
People like this trust me!

15:29.011 --> 15:30.971
I obviously have to say

15:29.011 --> 15:30.971
something nice back to them.

15:31.013 --> 15:32.973
This is why my family sucks.

15:33.015 --> 15:34.851
I have no training in this.

15:34.893 --> 15:38.354
This job...

15:38.396 --> 15:40.981
me... like.

15:41.023 --> 15:42.983
We're thrilled to have

15:41.023 --> 15:42.983
found you, Malcolm.

15:43.025 --> 15:44.985
The kids love you.

15:45.027 --> 15:46.613
You're great

15:45.027 --> 15:46.613
to have around.

15:46.654 --> 15:48.948
You've really become

15:46.654 --> 15:48.948
one of the family.

15:53.828 --> 15:55.872
I may not have been

15:53.828 --> 15:55.872
switched at birth,

15:55.914 --> 15:57.039
but I should have been.

15:57.081 --> 15:58.958
I love these people.

16:00.919 --> 16:02.712
(speaking Chinese)

16:49.091 --> 16:50.551
Okay, come on.

16:54.555 --> 16:56.015
Wait a minute.

17:00.102 --> 17:02.062
Sorry.

17:02.104 --> 17:03.523
Well...

17:03.564 --> 17:07.610
let's see what our

17:03.564 --> 17:07.610
little friend did today.

17:10.989 --> 17:13.574
(whistling)

17:19.622 --> 17:21.624
(blender whirs)

17:23.710 --> 17:25.712
(continues whistling)

17:47.567 --> 17:49.027
Oh, hi.

17:49.068 --> 17:50.110
Don't worry.

17:50.152 --> 17:51.320
I'd never hurt Barney.

17:51.362 --> 17:53.113
He's part of the family.

17:53.155 --> 17:55.115
Just like I'm part

17:53.155 --> 17:55.115
of the family, right?

17:55.157 --> 17:56.701
And since a big part

17:55.157 --> 17:56.701
of this family

17:56.743 --> 17:58.118
is being such a huge phony

17:58.160 --> 17:59.746
and launching

17:58.160 --> 17:59.746
secret investigations

17:59.787 --> 18:00.830
against each other,

18:00.872 --> 18:02.040
I thought I'd join in.

18:02.081 --> 18:04.166
Personal computers

18:02.081 --> 18:04.166
