18:04.208 --> 18:07.420
You can file tax returns,

18:04.208 --> 18:07.420
medical records,

18:07.461 --> 18:09.129
embarrassing private e-mail.

18:09.171 --> 18:11.131
Little security tip,

18:09.171 --> 18:11.131
